
Murandu idunhu riri munyika inonzi Burundi muAfrika.
MuchiNyanja, chiChewa, kiSwahili nemimwe mitauro yekuZambia,Kongo, Malawi nenyika zhinji dziri nechekumabvazuva kweAfrika, Murandu (Mulandu) zvinoreva kuti mhosva kana kuti muripo unenge watemerwa mutadzi. 

Munyika yeZimbabwe mune vanhu vanonzi vekwaMurandu vanowanikwa kwaMasembura, Chikwaka nekwaSeke pedyo naHanyani(Manyame)
